# No Cursor git attribution

Never add `Co-authored-by: Cursor`, `Made-with: Cursor`, or any Cursor attribution trailer to commits or pull requests.

When committing:
- Use plain `git commit -m "message"` only
- Never pass `--trailer` for Cursor attribution
- If a trailer was added by mistake, amend or rebase to remove it before finishing
